{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ecobin-api-collection-0001",
    "name": "EcoBin 接口（前端对接）",
    "description": "EcoBin 智慧环保回收箱后端接口集合。\n\n三端：网页·平台管理员、网页·租户、小程序·终端用户。\n\n使用方式：\n1. 在 Variables 中确认 baseUrl（默认 http://localhost:8080）。\n2. 先调用「认证」目录下的登录接口，响应会自动把 token 写入集合变量 adminToken / tenantToken / userToken。\n3. 其余目录已按角色绑定对应 token（folder 级 Bearer 认证），可直接调用。\n\n详见 docs/api-frontend.md。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "tenantToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userToken", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "认证（公开）",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "网页登录 - 管理员",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json && json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', json.data.token);",
                  "  console.log('adminToken 已保存');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userType\": \"admin\",\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/system/auth/login",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "system", "auth", "login" ]
            },
            "description": "平台管理员登录。userType=admin。成功后自动保存 adminToken。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "网页登录 - 租户",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json && json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantToken', json.data.token);",
                  "  console.log('tenantToken 已保存');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userType\": \"tenant\",\n  \"username\": \"greenadmin\",\n  \"password\": \"Green@123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/system/auth/login",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "system", "auth", "login" ]
            },
            "description": "租户登录。userType=tenant。成功后自动保存 tenantToken。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "小程序登录 - 微信",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json && json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userToken', json.data.token);",
                  "  console.log('userToken 已保存');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"微信 wx.login 返回的 code\",\n  \"appid\": \"租户的小程序 appid\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/system/auth/wx-login",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "system", "auth", "wx-login" ]
            },
            "description": "微信小程序登录。首次自动注册为普通用户(role=1)。成功后自动保存 userToken。"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
